{
  "stem": "894.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, uh-- you know, like, I really find it very funny, that everything he ate, I thought, I have to eat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I was about 5 feet 1' or 2', weighing 100 pounds, and he was 6 feet 2'.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I thought I have to eat-- everything he ate, I ate and enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that night I was quite sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was quite, quite sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I understand that some people literally died from overeating after having an empty stomach for a year.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this went on for awhile, not that long-- maybe four or six weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the neighbors would come in and say 'Heil Hitler!' And I would go 'Heil Hitler!' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did I use a different?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, because Kiss, in Hungarian-- in Hungarian, it actually means 'little.' 'Kicsit'-- 'kiss'-- not 'little.' 'Kicsit' would mean-- would mean 'little.' But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a kiss is a kiss, in any language.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGH] So it was not the Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I could say Renee Kiss is my name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we worked for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were decent to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did my job, and I-- I knew where I belonged, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a very lovely little town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my sister-- now and then, we would visit each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said to me, my Frenchman tells me that the war is going to be over any day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we started to get ready.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, while we rejoiced in our hearts, they were getting panicky, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so, one day I hear the German woman-- every day, they heard rumors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the war did come to an end, by the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
